BUILDING THE DOCS
=================
Make sure the right variables are (un)commented in the Makefile as
they control the paths used to find the DocBook schema and
style sheets.

Install the rights deps for your system. Again, check the Makefile for
details.


TARGETS
=======
    dist-clean - Runs 'clean' to get rid of garbage like *~ files and
    removes output from prior runs

    html/pdf/chunked - Create html/pdf/chunked html documents in the
    respective output/* folder

    docs - Create html & pdf & chunked html documents in the
    respective output/* folder


HELPERS
=======
    locator - Generates a proper schemas.xml file to help nxml-mode
    find your RelaxNG DocBook schemas.

